Update Release 9 (13.02.97)

This is the third generation of the Merlin Intuition-Emulation.

The archive contains both: An Update for Users of ProBench3 and a limited Demoversion for those who don't own ProBench3 by now.

ProBench3 features multiple screens and bitmaps in vga-memory at the same time and is highly compatible to applications which are written for the CyberGFX system (more informations inside).

