If you already own a full version of ProBench V3.1 you can skip this part! Continue at @{" Important " LINK "upd_eng" }

There are two major restrictions in this Demo-Version:

You can only use exactly 800 pixels wide screenmodes.

After approximal 30 minutes the Merlin-Blitter will be disabled and flashing colors will remind you on the demo nature of this package (you will be able to safe your work before reseting).

These are the only restrictions so you should be able to validate nearly all aspects of our emulation!

