@prev "demo_ger"
@next "adr_ger"
@endnode

@node "upd_eng" "DemoGuide"
@font topaz 8
@wordwrap

@{u}3. Important informations for future Updates@{uu}

Update 8 is the first Update which contains all files of the ProBench 3 distribution package. Further updates will base on this one until a new complete archive has been relesed. Please keep this archive for later use!

Installation of a new update consists of two major steps:

 1. By Patching the update 8 archive and generation of a new installation-directory in RAM:.
 2. By execution of the (new) installation script in the directory generated by step one.

After your update procedure is complette you can safely delete the temporary directory. Every new update (for now) is based on the archive "ProBench3-8.lha".

With this strategy you are able to skip updates without problems and we don't use so much space on public resources.

@{" Update History (German only) " LINK "changes" }

